ted\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/__lookupSetter__\"><code>Object.prototype.__lookupSetter__()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/hasOwnProperty\"><code>Object.prototype.hasOwnProperty()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/isPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.prototype.isPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/propertyIsEnumerable\"><code>Object.prototype.propertyIsEnumerable()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/setPrototypeOf\"><code>Object.setPrototypeOf()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toLocaleString\"><code>Object.prototype.toLocaleString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/toString\"><code>Object.prototype.toString()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Object/valueOf\"><code>Object.prototype.valueOf()</code></a></li></ol></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p>O método&nbsp;<code><strong>add()</strong></code>&nbsp;acrescenta um novo elemento com o valor especificado no final de um objeto&nbsp;<code>Set</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxe","title":"Sintaxe","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\"><code><em>mySet</em>.add(value);</code></pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parâmetros","title":"Parâmetros","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"value\">value</dt>\n <dd>Requerido. O&nbsp;valor de um elemento a ser adicionado ao objeto&nbsp;Set.</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valor_de_retorno","title":"Valor de retorno","isH3":true,"content":"<p><font face=\"Open Sans, Arial, sans-serif\">O objeto&nbsp;</font><code>Set</code>.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exemplos","title":"Exemplos","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"usando_o_método_add","title":"Usando o método <code>add</code>","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> mySet <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Set</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nmySet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">1</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nmySet<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token number\">5</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">add</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"some text\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token comment\">// pode ser encadeado</span>\n\nconsole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>mySet<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// Set [1, 5, \"some text\"]</span>\n</code></pre></div>","titleAsText":"Usando o método add"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificações","title":"Especificações","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Especificações</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Status</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Comentário</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/6.0/#sec-set.prototype.add\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript 2015 (6th Edition, ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Set.prototype.add' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-standard\">Padrão</span></td>\n   <td>Definição inicial.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://tc39.es/ecma262/#sec-set.prototype.add\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">ECMAScript (ECMA-262)<br><small lang=\"pt-BR\">The definition of 'Set.prototype.add' in that specification.</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">Padrão em tempo real</span></td>\n   <td></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatilidade_de_navegadores_(browser)","title":"Compatilidade de Navegadores (Browser)","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect2\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect3\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td>38</td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/13\" title=\"Released on 2012-06-05.\">13.0</a> (13.0)</td>\n   <td>11</td>\n   <td>25</td>\n   <td>7.1</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Feature</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Chrome for Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte Básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>38</td>\n   <td>13.0 (13.0)</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color:#f00;\">Não suportado</span></td>\n   <td>8</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas_específicas_para_firefox","title":"Notas específicas para Firefox","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li>Antes do&nbsp;Firefox 33 (Firefox 33 / Thunderbird 33 / SeaMonkey 2.30), <code>Set.prototype.add retornava</code>&nbsp;<code>undefined</code>&nbsp;e não era possível encadear chamadas. Isto foi resolvido (<a href=\"https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1031632\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">bug&nbsp;1031632</a>). O comportamento pode ser encontrado no Chrome/v8&nbsp;(<a href=\"https://code.google.com/p/v8/issues/detail?id=3410\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">issue</a>).</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"veja_também","title":"Veja também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Set\"><code>Set</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Set/delete\"><code>Set.prototype.delete()</code></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Set/has\"><code>Set.prototype.has()</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sintaxe","id":"sintaxe"},{"text":"Exemplos","id":"exemplos"},{"text":"Especificações","id":"especificações"},{"text":"Compatilidade de Navegadores (Browser)","id":"compatilidade_de_navegadores_(browser)"},{"text":"Notas específicas para Firefox","id":"notas_específicas_para_firefox"},{"text":"Veja também","id":"veja_também"}],"summary":"O método add() acrescenta um novo elemento com o valor especificado no final de um objeto Set.","popularity":0.0003,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Set.prototype.add()","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/set/add","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/pt-br/web/javascript/reference/global_objects/set/add/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web","title":"Tecnologia Web para desenvolvedores"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript","title":"JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference","title":"Referência JavaScript"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects","title":"Objetos Globais"},{"uri":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Set","title":"Set"},{"uri":